data.description: Welcome to your own slice of paradise! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath house is situated on a sprawling two-acre lot adorned with plants and trees, giving it a unique and enchanting Old Florida feel. The house itself exudes warmth and character, perfectly complementing the surrounding natural beauty. Step inside to a spacious open floor plan, where the living area flows into the dining space and kitchen creating an inviting and cheerful atmosphere. Located in Indian River Farms, you'll enjoy a serene and peaceful setting while being just a short drive away from modern conveniences.
